172
00:09:58,931 --> 00:10:02,034
No one can just get off the boat.

173
00:10:02,101 --> 00:10:03,202
We're all stuck there.

174
00:10:03,269 --> 00:10:06,405
Once you leave port, you can't go back.

175
00:10:06,472 --> 00:10:07,573
All of you

176
00:10:07,940 --> 00:10:10,676
have to make it to the goal.
That is how theater is.

177
00:10:11,911 --> 00:10:12,979
Go.

178
00:10:13,045 --> 00:10:14,614
<i>Being on the same boat</i>

179
00:10:14,680 --> 00:10:16,582
<i>and sharing the same fate...</i>

180
00:10:16,649 --> 00:10:19,619
<i>That applies to King & Prince
as a group as well.</i>

181
00:10:20,953 --> 00:10:22,455
<i>The two of them can work hard</i>

182
00:10:22,521 --> 00:10:25,324
<i>because no matter
how difficult things are,</i>

183
00:10:25,825 --> 00:10:28,327
<i>they have each other,
members who are determined</i>

184
00:10:28,594 --> 00:10:30,730
<i>to survive the rough waters together.</i>

185
00:10:32,398 --> 00:10:35,001
Ready...

186
