00:12:05,491 --> 00:12:07,560
-Tsukioka.
-Yes, I'm Chuya Tsukioka!

215
00:12:07,626 --> 00:12:09,862
I made it in time. That was close.

216
00:12:11,797 --> 00:12:13,199
-Chuya Tsukioka.
-Yes!

217
00:12:13,265 --> 00:12:15,868
I'm Chuya Tsukioka! I made it in time.

218
00:12:15,935 --> 00:12:16,836
That was close.

219
00:12:18,871 --> 00:12:19,772
Cut.

220
00:12:20,673 --> 00:12:23,142
Okay.

221
00:12:23,209 --> 00:12:24,643
<i>He somehow got it down.</i>

222
00:12:25,811 --> 00:12:27,012
Hey!

223
00:12:28,114 --> 00:12:29,014
Good morning.

224
00:12:29,448 --> 00:12:31,150
Yesterday...

225
00:12:33,052 --> 00:12:36,522
I was up late working on my manga.

226
00:12:36,589 --> 00:12:40,025
I was supposed to work on it today too,
but I finished it yesterday.

227
00:12:40,392 --> 00:12:42,561
